text: Metamulciber albostriatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1940.BioLib.cz - Metamulciber albostriatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1940
title: Metamulciber albostriatus
